title: Moody Blues
description:
Here is my collection of moody blues music.
contains 20 titles and includes:

a question of balance

days of future past

every good boy deserves a favour

go now

in search of the lost chord

journey into amazing caves

keys of the kingdom

long distant voyager

octave

on the threshold of a dream

seventh sojourn

strange times

sur la mer

the other side of life

the present

this is the moody blues (only a single track from disk 2 &#039;Simple Game&#039; which does not feature on any studio album)

to our children&#039;s children&#039;s children

also included solo albums by Justin Hayward
night flight
the veiw from the hill

Justin Hayward & John Lodge
blue jays

Ray Thomas solo album
from might oaks 

some cover art is included but not of the greatest quality.

happy listening
